00:22:26,130 --> 00:22:29,020
States, and my colleagues in the arts at Harvard

229
00:22:29,020 --> 00:22:33,470
could not have put better, as Mr. Cui put it, what the role of the arts

230
00:22:33,470 --> 00:22:37,870
is in a comprehensive education.

231
00:22:37,870 --> 00:22:38,965
Thank you very much.

